data.description: Cute and cozy cottage on Wixom Lake. Canal frontage with new dock ready for the lake life to return. Open concept floor plan creates a large living room space, with sliding glass doors that lead to the patio with great outdoor entertaining space. 2 car garage and 24x12 shed gives plenty of storage solutions for all of your outdoor toys. The perfect starter home or vacation getaway!
